OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers will break out across Argyll
OL,7,Fthrough the evening and night,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy and thundery.
OL,9,FMostly dry elsewhere with variable
OL,10,Famounts of cloud.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FA cloudy day with some showery
OL,13,Frain across Argyll, just the odd
OL,14,Fshower further south. Brightening up
OL,15,Fin the south later.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,18,FOutbreaks of rain will spread east on
OL,19,FSaturday, occasionally heavy later.
OL,20,FScattered showers on Sunday. Further
OL,21,Frain likely on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
